<li>Apply 'MDL-72923 message: Fixed levels of headings in messaging drawer'.</li>
<li>Fix 'Font on file storage admin type settings'.</li>
<li>Unix file endings - use 'find . -type f -print0 | xargs -0 dos2unix' in a Git Bash on Windows if you need to.</li>
</ol>

